---
// CoDesign.astro
---
<section id="values" class="values" aria-labelledby="values-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <ul class="values__grid" role="list">
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/TYPE/Part 3/Autonomy_image.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Autonomy</h3>
          <p>Supporting independent communication</p>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/TYPE/Part 3/Accessibility_image.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Accessibility</h3>
          <p>Designed with sensory, motor, and attentional needs in mind</p>
        </article>
      </li>
      <li>
        <article class="value-card">
          <img src="/assets/TYPE/Part 3/Co-Design_image.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>Co-Design</h3>
          <p>Built together with nonspeaking autistic collaborators</p>
        </article>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="values__cta">
      <a href="#process" class="btn">Explore</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="process" class="process" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
  <div class="process__inner section-inner">
    <div class="process__left">
      <h2 id="process-heading">Process with a purpose</h2>
      <img src="/assets/TYPE/Part 4/image_page4.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="process__right">
      <article>
        <h3>Co-design, not top-down</h3>
        <p>
          TYPE is developed with nonspeaking autistic people, not for them. Their lived experiences
          guide our decisions, ensuring the system addresses real needs, not assumptions.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Iterative &amp; Adaptive</h3>
        <p>
          Our process is flexible: we test, listen, and revise continuously. We value different paces
          of participation, allowing time for reflection and asynchronous contributions.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Transparency &amp; Trust</h3>
        <p>
          We are open about our progress and honest about challenges. Mutual respect and clear
          communication are at the heart of how we work.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .values {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
  }

  .values .section-inner {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .values__grid {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem);
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .value-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: transparent;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card img {
    width: 33vw;
    height: auto;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1.32;
    font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 1.8vw, 1.5rem);
    max-width: 19rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .values__cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 5rem;
  }

  .process {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    color: #111;
    padding-block: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .process__inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .process__left{
        display: flex;
        flex: 1;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
  }

  .process__left h2 {
    font-size: clamp(6rem, 6vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.93;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .process__left img {
    width:  100%
  }

  .process__right {
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content: space-around;
     gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
   
  }
  .process__right article {
    padding-block: 1.1rem;
    border-bottom: 0.125rem solid #777;
    &:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }

  .process__right h3 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.6vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .process__right p {
    color: #2a2a2a;
    line-height: 1.32;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 1.65vw, 2rem);
  }

  /* Tablet: 48rem (768px) */
  @media (max-width: 48rem) {
    .values {
      padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 3rem);
    }

    .values__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vh, 2rem);
    }

    .value-card img {
      width: clamp(15rem, 60vw, 25rem);
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    }

    .value-card p {
      font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.8vw, 1.2rem);
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .values__cta {
      /* margin-top: clamp(3rem, 5vh, 3.5rem); */
    }

    .process {
      padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 2.5rem);
    }

    .process__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: clamp(2rem, 4vh, 2.5rem);
    }

    .process__left h2 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .process__right h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    }

    .process__right p {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    }

    .process__right article {
      padding-block: 1rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile: 28rem (448px) */
  @media (max-width: 28rem) {
    .values {
      padding-block: 1.5rem;
    }

    .values__grid {
      gap: 0rem;
    }

    .value-card {
      gap: 0rem;
    }

    .value-card img {
      width: clamp(20rem, 50vw, 20rem);
      margin: 0
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.6rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .value-card p {
      font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 2vw, 1rem);
      max-width: 70%;
    }

    .values__cta {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    /* .values__cta .btn {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.45rem 1.2rem;
      min-height: 2.4rem;
    } */

    .process {
      padding-block: 1.5rem;
    }

    .process__inner {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .process__left {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process__left h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .process__right {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process__right h3 {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.6rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .process__right p {
      font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    }

    .process__right article {
      padding-block: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
